Here's a categorized list of **ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning)** software ‚Äî including **SAP and non-SAP ERP systems** ‚Äî with brief descriptions:

---

## üîπ **ERP Software List**

### ‚úÖ **SAP ERP Software**

| Software Name                       | Description                                                                                              |
| ----------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **SAP ECC** (ERP Central Component) | Legacy SAP ERP system used widely across enterprises.                                                    |
| **SAP S/4HANA**                     | Modern, in-memory ERP suite; successor of SAP ECC with advanced analytics and real-time data processing. |
| **SAP Business One**                | ERP for small and midsize businesses (SMEs).                                                             |
| **SAP Business ByDesign**           | Cloud ERP for mid-sized companies.                                                                       |
| **SAP R/3**                         | Earlier version of SAP ERP (now obsolete).                                                               |

---

### üö´ **Non-SAP ERP Software**

These are alternative ERP systems built by other vendors:

#### üî∑ **Large Enterprise ERP Systems**

| Software Name               | Vendor       | Notes                                                        |
| --------------------------- | ------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Oracle Fusion Cloud ERP** | Oracle       | Cloud-based ERP for finance, HR, and SCM.                    |
| **Microsoft Dynamics 365**  | Microsoft    | Modular ERP and CRM system, integrates with Microsoft stack. |
| **IFS Applications**        | IFS (Sweden) | Strong in aerospace, manufacturing, and field service.       |
| **Infor CloudSuite**        | Infor        | Industry-specific ERP (healthcare, manufacturing).           |
| **Workday**                 | Workday      | Cloud-based ERP focused on HCM and finance.                  |

#### üî∑ **Mid-Sized to Small Business ERP Systems**

| Software Name                | Vendor                  | Notes                                              |
| ---------------------------- | ----------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **NetSuite ERP**             | Oracle                  | Cloud-based ERP for growing businesses.            |
| **Tally ERP 9 / TallyPrime** | Tally Solutions (India) | Popular accounting & basic ERP in SMEs.            |
| **Zoho ERP (Zoho One)**      | Zoho Corporation        | Modular ERP for small businesses.                  |
| **Odoo**                     | Odoo (Open Source)      | Modular and open-source ERP, highly customizable.  |
| **ERPNext**                  | Frappe (India)          | Open-source ERP alternative to SAP & Odoo.         |
| **Sage X3 / Sage 300**       | Sage Group              | ERP for finance, distribution, and manufacturing.  |
| **Epicor ERP**               | Epicor                  | ERP for manufacturing and distribution industries. |
| **Syspro**                   | Syspro (South Africa)   | Manufacturing & distribution ERP.                  |

---

